  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdapterFactory
    Creates a driving or driving adapter which fulfills one of the following requirements: Public Default constructor available Public constructor with one Properties as attribute is available Public static factory method with return type of the requested interface Public static factory method with return type of the requested interface and Properties as argument If an adapter is created by its interface only a single implementation must be available.
